      <p style="text-transform: uppercase; color: #808080"><strong>Help us build gaming for enterprise</strong></p>
      <p>Outside of Esports, gaming skills receive little professional recongition. At Mapcontrol, we want to change that.</p>
      <p>We’re calling StarCraft players to discuss with us the skills you’ve honed in StarCraft and how these skills have shaped of your careers. In the process, we want to help you gain a more nuanced understanding of the value proposition of your gaming skills.</p>
      <p>If you’re a StarCraft player, we’d love to chat. To learn more about how we think about StarCraft and skill transfer or to schedule a conversation, you can connect with our team at <a href="">hi@mapcontro.io</a>.</p>
      <h4 class="reenter-text pb-3">A New Path for Gaming</h4>
      <p>Around the world, more and more people are playing video games. But outside of Esports, the skillsets players hone to master a game have received little professional recognition. At Mapcontrol, we strive to take gaming skillsets to the same level of professional recognition as skills honed through work experience and education. Our mission is to bring gaming from consumer into enterprise.</p>
      <p>No game aligns better with our mission than StarCraft. If you’re a StarCraft player, you know the manifold challenges that the game's complexity holds and the strategic aptitude and self-reflective perserverance it takes to excel at competitive StarCraft. We believe these skills can chart a new path for gaming. Gaming for enterprise.</p>
      <h4 class="reenter-text pb-3">How We Want to Collaborate</h4>
      <p>We’re currently researching how StarCraft players build impactful careers. We'd be excited to augment this research with your experience. In turn, we want to share our research with you and help you think in novel ways about the skills you’ve honed in StarCraft.</p>
      <p>We’d love to champion your story, answer your questions and walk you through gaming for enterprise. If you’re excited about charting a new path for gaming, we want to connect with you.</p>
      <p>Let’s build a new meta. For careers and for enterprise.</p>
